import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-fetch-data', templateUrl: './fetch-data.component.html' }) export class FetchDataComponent { public bots: IBot[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get('http://localhost:7234/api/Bots').subscribe(result => { this.bots = result.items; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface IBots { items: IBot[] } interface IBot { id: string, business: string, city: string, region: string, country: string, lat: number, lon: number, dateModified: Date, dateCreated: Date, }
